Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:48.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}「人とは違う」で差をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}コンビニの雑誌コーナー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}表紙にふとして書いてあった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:59.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:02.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}子供の頃は気にもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}気に入らなければ怒って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:08.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}好きなものを好きだと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:12.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕らは変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}守りたいものが変わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されない宝物から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されるための建前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:25.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}大人になるほど　後悔する生き物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:28.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}でもね　それでもね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}見えるものがあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:39.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}だから僕は僕らしく　そして君は君らしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:45.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}初めから　探すようなものではないんだと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:51.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕は君じゃないし　君も僕じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}すれ違う　手をつなぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:58.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}そこには愛だって生まれる　そういうもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:08.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変えられない　大切があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:12.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変わりゆく生活が　正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.41,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling wide to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:45.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:56.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}But it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:02.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:06.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:14.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the times we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:22.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That the words in our hands we will draw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:30.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Maybe it wasn't 'cause\N you're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:41.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Every moment, everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:47.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can feel, I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:52.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding you from bad
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:59.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You will learn
